#Welcome to PYTGPT-BOT.
#For chatting, text-to-image and text-to-voice conversions.

#Usage commands:
#1. /start : Show this help info 📚
#2. /chat : Chat with AI 🤖
#3. /image : Generate image from text 🖼️ (default)
#4. /prodia : Generate image from text 🎨 (Prodia)
#5. /audio : Generate audio from text 🎧
#6. /intro : Set new text for chat intro 📝
#7. /voice : Set new voice for speech synthesis 🎙️
#8. /provider : Set new chat provider 🌐
#9. /awesome : Set awesome prompt as intro 💥
#10. /history : Check chat history 🕰️
#11. /check : Check current settings ⚙️
#12. /reset : Start new chat thread 🔄
#13. /myid : Echo your Telegram ID 🆔
#default : Chat with AI.

#For instances :
#   /chat Hello there.
#   /image Sunset view from ISS
#   /prodia Clear cool shore view
#   /audio I am better than you.


#Admin Commands
#/clear : Clear all chats 🧹
#/total : Total chats available 📊
#/drop : Clear entire chat table and bot logs 🗑️
#/sql : Run sql statements against database 📊
#/logs : View bot logs 📜

